  <title>Change Employee Password</title>

  <p>Only administrators can change the password of an employee.</p>

  <p>To change the password of an employee:</p>
  <steps>
    <item><p>Log in to the Control Panel.</p></item>
    <item><p>Click the <gui style="tab">Employees</gui> tab.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select the employee you want to change the password from the list.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">Edit</gui><gui style="menuitem">Change Password</gui></guiseq> or click <gui style="button">Change Password</gui> in the toolbar.</p></item>
    <item><p>Enter the password.</p></item>
    <item><p>Enter the password again to verify, then click <gui style="button">Save</gui>.</p></item>
  </steps>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>You may also right-click on the list to show the context menu instead, where you could select <gui style="menuitem">Change Password</gui> to change the password of the currently selected employees.</p>
  </note>

